oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Diary of Roysdon Roberson Etter, Co., H, 16th Tenn. Inf. Regt., CSA
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Diary of Roysdon Roberson Etter, Co. H, 16th Tenn. Inf. Regt., CSA. This diary is from Sept. 1861 to October 4, 1862. Other volumes of his diary are on microfilm at TSLA. Soldier was from Viola, Warren Co., Tenn. Etter was wounded at Perryville, Ky. in October 1862.
